#: Game.Levels.HomPset
msgid "Welcome to the **Homomorphism Problem Set** вҖ” practice under reduced\n"
"scaffolding.\n"
"\n"
"You have all the tools from the last two worlds: В§0, В§1,\n"
"В§2, В§3, kernel and range membership lemmas, В§4,\n"
"В§5, В§6, and В§7.\n"
"\n"
"No new theorems or tactics here (except В§8 in the\n"
"final levels вҖ” the natural dual of В§9). The focus\n"
"is applying familiar moves to fresh problem surfaces.\n"
"\n"
"The boss: prove that a homomorphism is surjective if and only if its\n"
"range is the whole group вҖ” the dual of the Kernel and Image boss:\n"
"\n"
"| Property | Subgroup condition |\n"
"|----------|--------------------|\n"
"| **Injective** | В§10 (proved!) |\n"
"| **Surjective** | В§11 (your target) |"
msgstr ""

