"and transitivity вҖ” into a single В§0 structure.\n"
"\n"
"An В§1 bundles:\n"
"- В§2\n"
"- В§3\n"
"- В§4\n"
"\n"
"Use В§5 to split into three subgoals. Each subgoal\n"
"is a proof you completed in the last three levels."
msgstr ""

