"then shoes, you take off shoes first, then socks. The \"inverse\" of\n"
"doing В§3 then В§4 is undoing В§5 then undoing В§6.\n"
"\n"
"**Strategy**: cancel from the inside out. Use В§7 to strip the\n"
"outer parentheses, then use targeted В§8 to isolate В§9\n"
"in the middle. After canceling that, В§10 remains.\n"
"\n"
"Use a В§11 block to show each step."
msgstr ""

