#: Game.Levels.HomComposition.L07_Boss
msgid "Congratulations on completing **Homomorphism Composition**!\n"
"\n"
"You proved: **if В§0 is injective, then В§1 is injective**.\n"
"\n"
"The argument:\n"
"В§2\n"
"\n"
"Notice the contrapositive reading: if В§3 collapsed two elements\n"
"(В§4 with В§5), then В§6 would also collapse them\n"
"(В§7). So if В§8 never collapses, В§9\n"
"never collapses either.\n"
"\n"
"The converse is false: В§10 injective does NOT imply В§11 is\n"
"injective. For example, let В§12 send В§13\n"
"and В§14 send В§15. Then В§16 is the\n"
"identity (injective!), but В§17 collapses В§18 and В§19.\n"
"\n"
"There's also a kernel-based proof of the boss: since\n"
"В§20 (Level 2) and В§21 (because\n"
"В§22 is injective), we get В§23, hence В§24,\n"
"hence В§25 is injective. This connects the first half of the world\n"
"(kernel/range containment) to the second half (injectivity/surjectivity\n"
"transfer).\n"
"\n"
"This asymmetry вҖ” injectivity transfers to the **inner** map,\n"
"surjectivity transfers to the **outer** map вҖ” is the\n"
"**inner/outer transfer** pattern.\n"
"\n"
"Summary of composition properties:\n"
"\n"
