#: Game.Levels.HomPset.L07_Boss
msgid "Congratulations on completing the **Homomorphism Problem Set**!\n"
"\n"
"You proved the dual of the Kernel and Image boss:\n"
"\n"
"> **A group homomorphism is surjective if and only if its range\n"
"> is the whole group.**\n"
"\n"
"The two fundamental equivalences together:\n"
"\n"
"| Property | Algebraic condition | Subgroup condition |\n"
"|----------|--------------------|--------------------|\n"
"| **Injective** | В§0 | В§1 |\n"
"| **Surjective** | В§2 | В§3 |\n"
"\n"
"And the proof structures are duals:\n"
"- The В§4 proof used В§5 to convert between В§6 and В§7.\n"
"- The В§8 proof used В§9 to convert between В§10 and В§11.\n"
"\n"
"A homomorphism that is both injective and surjective is an **isomorphism** вҖ”\n"
"a perfect structural match between two groups. You'll formalize isomorphisms\n"
"later in the course.\n"
"\n"
"Your skills from these three worlds:\n"
"\n"
"| Move | Pattern |\n"
"|------|---------|\n"
"| **Hom-property** | Push В§12 through with В§13, В§14, В§15 |\n"
"| **Kernel reasoning** | В§16 вҶ’ algebra вҶ’ В§17 |\n"
"| **Image reasoning** | В§18 witness вҶ’ В§19 new witness вҶ’ verify |\n"
"| **Kernel navigation** | В§20, В§21, В§22 |\n"
"| **Range navigation** | В§23, В§24, В§25 |\n"
"\n"
"On paper: *Forward: if В§26, then for any В§27,\n"
"В§28, so there exists В§29 with В§30.\n"
"Backward: if В§31 is surjective, then for any В§32, there exists\n"
"В§33 with В§34, i.e., В§35, so В§36.*\n"
"\n"
"What's next: you'll study how homomorphisms interact with\n"
"composition вҖ” does the composition of two injective homomorphisms\n"
"remain injective? What about surjective ones?"
msgstr ""

