#: Game.Levels.HomSubgroups.L07_Boss
msgid "Congratulations on completing **Homomorphism Subgroups**!\n"
"\n"
"You proved the **Galois connection** between В§0 and В§1:\n"
"\n"
"> **В§2**\n"
"\n"
"This says that В§3 and В§4 are adjoint operations: pushing\n"
"forward and pulling back are interchangeable when asking about\n"
"containment.\n"
"\n"
"On paper: *Let В§5 be a homomorphism, В§6, В§7.\n"
"Then В§8 iff В§9. Forward: if В§10, then\n"
"for any В§11, В§12, so В§13. Backward:\n"
"if В§14, take В§15, write В§16 for some\n"
"В§17, so В§18, i.e., В§19.*\n"
"\n"
"Notice the **comap/map asymmetry**: the forward direction is easier\n"
"because it reduces the hard operation (image: produce a witness) to\n"
"the easy one (preimage: check a property). This is the core benefit\n"
"of the adjunction вҖ” it translates image questions into preimage\n"
"questions.\n"
"\n"
"The Galois connection implies both unit laws:\n"
"- В§20 (take В§21, forward direction)\n"
"- В§22 (Level 6, take В§23, backward)\n"
"\n"
"Summary of В§24 and В§25:\n"
"\n"
"| Operation | Membership | Direction | Special case |\n"
"|-----------|-----------|-----------|--------------|\n"
"| В§26 | В§27 | Pull back (target вҶ’ source) | В§28 |\n"
"| В§29 | В§30 | Push forward (source вҶ’ target) | В§31 |\n"
"\n"
"Proof moves learned:\n"
"- **Hom-through-comap**: unfold В§32, apply hom property, close with subgroup closure\n"
"- **Image witness selection**: unfold В§33, provide В§34\n"
"- **Galois adjunction**: В§35\n"
"\n"
"Looking ahead: you'll next study cosets and normal subgroups. The\n"
"preimage operation returns when you prove that the preimage of a\n"
"normal subgroup is normal вҖ” a key step toward quotient groups."
msgstr ""

