#: Game.Levels.SubgroupBasics.L11_Boss
msgid "Congratulations on completing **Subgroup Basics**!\n"
"\n"
"You built the intersection of two subgroups from scratch, proving all\n"
"three closure properties. Each closure proof followed the same pattern:\n"
"\n"
"1. **Destructure** the В§0 hypothesis with В§1\n"
"2. **Apply** the membership lemma (В§2, В§3, В§4)\n"
"   to each component separately\n"
"3. **Rebuild** the conjunction with В§5\n"
"\n"
"This is the **component-wise membership** pattern: when the carrier\n"
"involves В§6, prove each part independently and recombine. You'll\n"
"see it again whenever intersections or conjunctive conditions appear.\n"
"\n"
"On paper, the В§7 proof would read: *\"Let В§8.\n"
"Then В§9 and В§10. Since В§11 is a subgroup, В§12.\n"
"Since В§13 is a subgroup, В§14. Hence В§15.\"* The\n"
"В§16 steps correspond to \"Then В§17 and В§18\", and\n"
"the angle-bracket rebuild corresponds to \"Hence В§19\".\n"
"\n"
"Your new tools from this world:\n"
"\n"
"| Item | Type |\n"
"|------|------|\n"
"| В§20 | Subgroup containment |\n"
"| В§21 | Trivial subgroup В§22 |\n"
"| В§23 | Whole group |\n"
"| В§24 | Intersection of subgroups |\n"
"| В§25 | В§26 |\n"
"| В§27 | В§28 (always true) |\n"
"| В§29 | В§30 |\n"
"| В§31 | Destructure В§32 and В§33 hypotheses |\n"
"| В§34 | Prove subgroup equality by membership |\n"
"| В§35 | Partially fill in terms with В§36 placeholders |\n"
"\n"
"Looking ahead: the **center** of a group вҖ” the set of elements\n"
"commuting with everything вҖ” is a subgroup you can locate in this\n"
"lattice. And the question \"is the kernel equal to В§37?\" will\n"
"characterize injective homomorphisms. The lattice isn't just\n"
"abstract structure вҖ” it's the language for the major theorems ahead.\n"
"\n"
"In the next world, you'll practice these tools on varied examples."
msgstr ""

